sql:
SELECT product_id, product_name, product_price, product_color
FROM Products
WHERE product_id IN (
    SELECT product_id
    FROM Order_Items
    GROUP BY product_id
    HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT order_id) < 2
)
OR product_id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT product_id FROM Order_Items)
question: What are the id, name, price and color of the products which have not been ordered for at least twice?

sql:
SELECT 
    p.product_id, 
    p.product_name, 
    p.product_price, 
    p.product_color
FROM 
    Products p
LEFT JOIN 
    Order_Items oi ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
GROUP BY 
    p.product_id, p.product_name, p.product_price, p.product_color
HAVING 
    COUNT(oi.order_item_id) < 2;
